VENTRILOQUISM: Throwing your voice

Category: Creative
Base skill: 16% (+4%/level, cap 98%)

Speaking without visibly moving your lips, convincingly enough that
an audience believes the voice is coming from somewhere else, such as
a puppet or a spot across the room. A performance skill with obvious
uses for a con artist too.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, singing, disguise
